<a name="lectures">
<h3>Lecture Synopses</h3> 

  <p>

  <table border=1 cellpadding=3 cellspacing=1>
  <colgroup align=right> </colgroup>
  <tr>
    <th style="color:blue">L#</th>
    <th style="color:blue">Date</th>
    <th style="color:blue">Topic</th>
  </tr><tr>
    <td> 1 </td>
    <td> Jan 5 </td>
    <td> Probability distributions; the definition of entropy </td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td> 2 </td>
    <td> Jan 10 </td>
    <td> Conditional entropy; mutual information; KL-divergence; 
      basic properties (some proofs via Jensen's inequality)
    </td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td> 1 </td>
    <td> Jan 12 </td>
    <td> Entropy and data compression; uniquely decodable codes and
      prefix-free codes; Kraft inequality; Shannon codes </td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td> 1 </td>
    <td> Jan 18 </td>
    <td> Arithmetic coding and its analysis, without regard to
      implementation issues </td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td> 1 </td>
    <td> Jan 19 </td>
    <td> Communication protocols; deterministic and randomized (private
      as well as public coin) communication complexity </td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td> 1 </td>
    <td> Jan 24 </td>
    <td> Information complexity; the cost of transmitting one bit and
      its consequences </td>
  </tr></table>

